				dumb question.  If you're playing on an exchange server, you have the same exact right to ebay stuff as the next guy (in this case the people you're grouping with).  It's no more exploitive than people say... grouping to get loot that would be an upgrade for their character.  We all pick and choose camps based on loots, even the ubers do, when a new expansion rolls out; there's always SOMETHING worthwhile at particular camps.
<br />

<br />
If you're playing on an Exchange server, you can pretty much assume the worst of the person next to you; that they're Yantis incarnate.<br />
