				That's an interesting way to look at it (RE: the mob hunter quote). If someone gets an item that sells for $100 on this new exchange thing just because they rolled a 80 to my 70 then that's a bit stupid. If you want to make a server where people can profit then do it like WoW quest items: everyone gets a "copy" of the item.
